snippet.title: AfterHours - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The first After Hours trailer shows off the latest gruesome and scary gameplay for Survival-Horror nerds.

Check out our Steam Page and make sure to add it to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1884540/AfterHours/



Song Used: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a5N99v5VmPk
